title: Forgotten Temple of the Blood Baron
story: For years the temple of the Blood Baron was considered lost. Now it is controlled by a party of hobgoblins.

notes.text: A lavishly decorated door with a keyhole to the south.
A fresco on the ceiling, makes a person slightly bigger when looked at.
An enchanted gem at the bottom of a pool.
A stuffed gnome hunter with a weird, made of an unknown material scarf in their hands.
A carving depicting the landscape around the temple as it looked in the distant past.
